             вҶ’ is-equiv (вҷӯ-map (postcomp-О  (Оұ вҲҳ x))))
      вҶ’ is-fibrewise-equiv Оұ
  cubes-separate-fibrewise Оұ eq
    = is-fibrewise-equivвҶҗfamily-separates-with-рқҹҷ
        в–Ў^_
        cubes-separate
        Оұ
        {0} single!
        (О» _ вҶ’ eq)

